The bivariate Clayton copula with parameter \(\theta &gt; 0\) is defined by, for all \((u,v)\in ]0,1]^2\), \[
C_{\theta}\left( u, v \right) = \left( u^{-\theta} + v^{-\theta} - 1  \right)^{- \frac{1}{\theta}}
\]

